Do I have to worry because they are enlarged or should I relax because they are all negative? 1st Dx 2004, right breast, 11cm tumor, node negative, triple neg, BRCA1. 2nd Dx 2009, left breast, 2 tumors, 11/30 nodes, triple neg.
